Fork of NetBSD Larn for Linux: https://github.com/r7st/larn

Notable Changes:
Builds on MacOS - not just Linux
Standing on items/stairs/fountains/etc. does not prompt for interaction unless you press 'g'.
Charisma stat improves/worsens shop prices by 1% per level above/below 12.
Saves can be backed up without the game considering it cheating.

Compile with:
MAKESYSPATH=mk bmake

Play with:
./larn

- r7st (r7st.guru@gmail.com)
